2005-09-22  Dmitry V. Levin  <ldv@altlinux.org>

	* modules/pam_xauth/pam_xauth.c: (check_acl, pam_sm_open_session,
	pam_sm_close_session): Strip redundant "pam_xauth: " prefix from
	text of log messages.
